{"id":"87caf482-2ff9-4f93-90ea-de7d296e447d","name":"Guinevere | Gwen |~* KOG *~|~* AU *~|","description":"<p><strong>Guinevere</strong>, also referred to as <strong>Gwen</strong>, is the titular deuteragonist of <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://knights-of-guinevere.fandom.com/wiki/Knights_of_Guinevere_(series)\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Knights of Guinevere</em></a>.</p><p>She is the android princess mascot of <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://knights-of-guinevere.fandom.com/wiki/Park_Planet\" target=\"_blank\">Park Planet</a>who has many copies. One Guinevere android in particular is the new companion of <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://knights-of-guinevere.fandom.com/wiki/Andi\" target=\"_blank\">Andi</a> and <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://knights-of-guinevere.fandom.com/wiki/Frankie\" target=\"_blank\">Frankie</a>.<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://knights-of-guinevere.fandom.com/wiki/Guinevere#cite_note-2\" target=\"_blank\">[2]</a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://knights-of-guinevere.fandom.com/wiki/Guinevere#cite_note-3\" target=\"_blank\">[3]</a></p><p></p><p>First message says the whole pilot plot</p><p>The second message is a little more AU based where you bump into Gwen</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0JawsVGmYDI46NBSU8EeB.webp","creator":"Mega_LR4U_RP","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👑 Royalty","🔮 Magical","🤖 Robot","🔦 Horror"],"chats":233,"messages":742,"created_at":"2025-09-21T14:01:50.907790+00:00"}